title: Fudgy brownies with chocolate icing
ingredients: ['Brownies', '200g dark chocolate, chopped, divided', '120g butter', '300g caster sugar', '3 eggs', '60g plain flour', '30g cocoa powder', 'Icing', '125g icing sugar', '45g butter, room temperature', '3 tablespoons cocoa powder', '3 teaspoons honey', '1 tablespoon milk, or more as needed']
